title: Ellemtel and the axe - Ericsson
snippet: Ellemtel Utvecklings AB was established in May 1970 as a company owned jointly by L.M. Ericsson and Televerket. Over the following year both companies focused on formulating specifications for the joint exchange. It was a meeting of two worlds.
